wiked-diff-empty: This message appears instead of a "diff" when comparing two revisions that are identical.
wiked-diff-same: This text or symbol is the title attribute (popup) for the "wiked-diff-empty" message.
wiked-diff-ins: This text or symbol is the title attribute (popup) for insertion blocks.
wiked-diff-del: This text or symbol is the title attribute (popup) for deletion blocks.
wiked-diff-block-left: This text or symbol is the title attribute (popup) for moved blocks with their origin mark to the left.
wiked-diff-block-right: This text or symbol is the title attribute (popup) for moved blocks with their origin mark to the right.
wiked-diff-block-left-nounicode: This text or symbol is the non-UniCode alternative for the "wiked-diff-block-left" text or symbol for legacy browsers.
wiked-diff-block-right-nounicode: This text or symbol is the non-UniCode alternative for the "wiked-diff-block-right" text or symbol for legacy browsers.
